data.title: Ok food, high prices, dirty restrooms...
data.text: This place took the place of a restaurant that went out of business. The food had good flavor, but the portion was small considering the price. The salad bar was a waste, looked like a bag of salad mix from Costco, and four dressings! Not worth the added price to the meal. The .99 coffee was really good! The staff was friendly, and helpful. The restroom was dirty, and being only open two days prior to our visit, already had a really bad odor! Around the corner to this place is Tommy's Cafe, which we eat at all the time, ten times better, at a lower cost...
